    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the chicken is done, transfer the <strong>cooked chicken</strong> to a clean board and shred apart using two forks – this technique is known as 'pulling'</p><p>Return the <strong>pulled chicken</strong> back to the pan with the <strong>mashed roasted garlic</strong>, <strong>drained tortiglioni</strong>,<strong> roasted courgette</strong>,<strong> chopped spinach </strong>and a splash of <strong>starchy pasta water</strong></p><p>Give everything a good mix up – this is your <strong>roasted garlic & pulled chicken tortiglioni</strong></p>",
